## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="38783-104">属性或字段必须是公共的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38783-104">The property or field must be public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="38783-105">包含属性的类都必须标记为<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38783-105">The class that contains the property must be marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="38783-106">将不会检测任何字段或类中未用这个或另一个 WMI 提供程序扩展特性标记的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38783-106">Any fields or properties in the class that are not marked with this or another WMI Provider Extensions attribute will not be instrumented.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="38783-107">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementProbe 属性以指示字段表示只读的 WMI 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38783-107">The following example shows how to use the ManagementProbe attribute to indicate that a field represents a read-only WMI property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[ManagementProbe]  
string count;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="38783-108">下一个示例演示如何使用 ManagementProbe 属性可将属性标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="38783-108">The next example shows how to use the ManagementProbe attribute to mark a property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementProbe attribute to specify that a property  
// is a read-only property in the provider. Consumers will be  
// able to get this property value through WMI.  
[ManagementProbe]  
public int ReadOnlyProperty  
{  
    get { return this.propertyValue; }  
}  
```
